{{en-verb|leaps|leaping|leaped|past2=leapt|past3=lept|past3_qual=archaic|past4=lope|past4_qual=archaic|leaped|past_ptc2=leapt|past_ptc3=lopen|past_ptc3_qual=archaic}}

